Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影月已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不存在于这世上的任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:02:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风中之烛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香铃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.97,0:02:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是马上送回村庄比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 我来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧一直不退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识仍然不清
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来应该受了相当大的打击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最主要的是无法感觉到她还活着的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像没有魂魄的躯壳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶老师 香铃她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香铃能治好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把热降下来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就好好照顾她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香铃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上最重要的影月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样在自己眼前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影月大人 影月大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 香铃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是一味地依靠你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待着你能救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你也知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影月的生命只剩下最后一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最最重要并珍爱的另一个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的 做你自己喜欢的就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 那女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影月还真是被大家爱着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类真是无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和影月永远都爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份心意会留给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳月 谢谢你给我生命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了件很不合自己风格的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道吧 还有最后一个方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要为这家伙做到那种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你白痴啊 既然早就做到那种地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还说那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 在国试前看到你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和宵都不敢相信自己的眼睛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这不是很好么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你最擅长的就是心血来潮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正再长也不过五十年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我们来说 不过是一转眼的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔偷偷溜出来的时间还是有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候我就带上好酒去找你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香铃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香铃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香铃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影月大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳月又给了我生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是可以活到寿命终结的长度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时候为止 能和我在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香铃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时候 我已经是老婆婆了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时候我也是老公公了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你再次消失的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香铃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳月再次赋予的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论到何时 都请保佑影月大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天也快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 这个村子也快迎来春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的春天似乎特别早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了祝福两位的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请安息吧 好好休息 堂主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 怪病真的已经根除了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到那个女州牧居然能活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又立了大功吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要阻止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要火速采取行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过分 明知道朕很弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有些生疏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就气喘吁吁了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也稍微手下留情点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想手下留情的话 您也不会来我这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在稍微好点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知什么时候起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多了很多不能舍弃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后的最后也要追求胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您作为紫刘辉需要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统统夺过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我觉得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的处置是必要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:13:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么总觉得朕老是在做让秀丽讨厌的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是会因为这种事就讨厌您的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能平安回来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一直忍耐着等她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这样…就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据调查 红、杜两位州牧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部放弃了州牧的权限而赶往现地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是红州牧 已经连续两次放弃权限了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说她完全不明白州牧这个位置的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些许多不合州牧身份的不负责且轻率的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣以为绝对不能纵容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:14:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即刻解除红秀丽和杜影月的茶州州牧职务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由现任黑州州牧櫂瑜代替他们的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫂瑜立刻赶往茶州
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快进行交接并维护茶州的安定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜影月降职 由櫂瑜担任他的监护人及老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他作为辅佐好好学习
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是降职啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是为了他将来出人头地铺路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 对红官吏的处置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕命她完成交接后尽快返回贵阳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剥夺她所有官衔 暂不准上朝议事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下一个职位任命之前 先做冗官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀丽他们将事后处理委托给丙太守
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到了琥琏城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 阳月大人已经
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他与我交换
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入熟睡状态 已经不会再出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再出现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝酒也不会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为睡得很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算是最喜欢的酒也无法让他醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能永远和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说啊 那时候没能说出的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是金鱼的粪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是在说影月大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算找到你了 影月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:17:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 龙莲 之前真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气氛那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现了伏兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还夺取了好友的宝座
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人的自尊不允许这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得再次见面了 就和我一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想和你分开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙莲 刚才的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会突然出现鸽子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旅行途中和杂技团学的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾 这个只能表演一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等再抓到鸽子才能表演
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样抓到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我一吹笛子 就看到啪啪地落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是受了什么刺激呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 那么再去抓鸽子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香铃不一起去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会输呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你来了啊 金鱼的粪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想被你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香铃和龙莲谁是金鱼的粪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺绣是…那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能偷偷教我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点就可以 能绣出樱花的花瓣就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 做法我是知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我对刺绣很不擅长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起绣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 珠翠 好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没好呢 圣上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕也是绣了一半
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 互相看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互交换
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在缝抹布吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我都说不喜欢这个了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕的比你的好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石荣村的人都渐渐回来了 也开始重建
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说丙太守不辞辛劳 亲自上阵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从王都来的医生们 大多留在茶州
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为当地医术的复兴而努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设立学术机关的费用 也请务必协助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这些家伙发起的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然要全力协助了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连日的操劳还真累人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕青
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你胆敢胡乱捏她鼻子把她弄醒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是要生气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是帮她盖好毯子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我几岁了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静兰 有没有找到什么线索
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那些逃走的缥家的术士们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知他们用了什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踪迹完全被抹去 一点线索都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够辨别身份的东西呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线索全断了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情陷入谜团中了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要写报告的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说一个奇怪的少年与疾病搏斗 失败
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后完结
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像蜥蜴断掉的尾巴一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这两人折磨到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:21:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 明知道犯人是谁却无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是缥家的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵阳的信送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是任免令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啦 新手官吏的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经算是手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 反正现在都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.97,0:21:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 先不说我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要秀丽做冗官 也有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冗官是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不怎么好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冗官就是只有官吏之名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何实权和职务的虚职
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:22:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是错了 她也是通过了严酷考试而及第的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能就这样扔到一边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在朝议上决定的 也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过分 太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看错圣上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 他到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许这是先发制人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人对秀丽这次的功绩心怀不轨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.45,0:22:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是给那些人的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.43,0:22:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了 太残酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 谢谢了 香铃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.03,0:22:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许因为香铃你不在的时候 我有些乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.61,0:22:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒觉得没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我什么都没做 却只是降职
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.89,0:22:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还由櫂州牧继任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.02,0:22:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救了大家的秀丽却如此下场…真是太…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:22:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说没关系了 别在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.44,0:23:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是想让我休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.09,0:23:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这解释不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 对了 今晚要吃猪肉火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.54,0:24:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被解除了茶州州牧的职务
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.85,0:24:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,250)}人生无常
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.05,0:24:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我一点都不后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.81,0:24:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是尽力做了力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.20,0:24:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会难得 在回贵阳之前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.62,0:24:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先在茶州游览一下吧
